The '''Baobab family''' was one of the galaxy's oldest and most affluent clans. Hailing from the planet [[Manda/Legends|Manda]], the Baobabs had become known for both the [[Baobab Archives]] and their [[Baobab Merchant Fleet]], one of the finest trading flotillas in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. Notable members of the Baobab family included [[Mungo Baobab]], [[Oggem Baobab|"Old Ogger" Baobab]], [[Ebenn Q3 Baobab/Legends|Ebenn Q3 Baobab]], [[Pookie Baobab]], and the father of [[Binary/Legends|droidspeak]], [[Yperio Baobab]].

[[Crix Q5 Baobab]] was an officer candidate instructor at the [[Baobab Merchant Marine Academy]] on [[Manda/Legends|Manda]].

